<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.5.7">
<l>puḷḷiṉai vāypiḷantu pūṅkuruntam cāyttu</l>
<l>tuḷḷi viḷaiyāṭit tūṅkuṟi veṇṇeyai</l>
<l>yaḷḷiya kaiyā laṭiyēṉ mulaineruṭum</l>
<l>piḷḷaip pirāṉkoṭṭāy cappāṇi</l>
<l>pēymulai yuṇṭāṉē cappāṇi.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Lord child who caressed the breasts of [this] servant, me, with the hands</l>
<l>Which scooped butter from the hanging pot-net, skipping and playing,</l>
<l>Having pushed over the budding kuruntu [tree],</l>
<l>And split the bird’s mouth, clap your hands;</l>
<l rend="indent">you who suckled the demon’s breast, clap your hands!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
